    step1_title:"Exercise 1 — Entry questionnaire “The Europe I know”",
    step1_html:"Individual answers, written on a sheet, are used for a collegial review of the starting situation and to spark interest in the topic. The <strong>Brainstorming</strong> method is used (slides 1-2).",
