    step3_html:"<strong>2a)</strong> each participant raises one of three coloured cards to identify the competence shown (a quick, dynamic activity). <strong>2b)</strong> sentence completion to match sources with functions. <strong>2c)</strong> a <em>true/false</em> questionnaire in groups of three, to discuss how the sources of EU law work.",
    step4_title:"Sources of law and EU legislation (slides 8-16)",
