    sg_s4_title:"Plenary discussion", sg_s4_text:"Suggested order: the <strong>Commission</strong> reworks and presents the proposal → the <strong>Parliament</strong> comments and proposes amendments → the <strong>Council</strong> assesses and negotiates → the <strong>Citizens</strong> react and apply pressure. The facilitator gives the floor, keeps time and stimulates debate.",
